{
  "stem": "4187.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "She's living like a human being.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "She's probably going to cook for her husband for lunch in a number of, you know, in hours.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "What I'm trying to say is that the realization that there are still people out there living like human beings.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And here we are in this cattle truck being-- in-- in this unbelievable, dreadful situation-- taken somewhere where we don't know where.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It was enough to send you crazy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "It really was.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "You know, I don't know whether-- it-- it-- and-- and I don't know if anyone-- if everyone gets claustrophobic.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I do.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And that feeling of claustrophobia, of being shut in, in the hands-- even though you weren't, of course, literally-- but in the hands of these animals-- I wish I could tell you.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I can't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "It is not possible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "You know, the panic, the-- the fear, the unbelievable terror that was gripping one.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And it wasn't that it was for two minutes, and then it'd be all right.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "It was just growing and growing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Anyway, when we arrived in Auschwitz-- at least when we arrived, we didn't know where-- by then, people were fainting, and people were-- it was-- by then, it was fairly quiet, because it was spent.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "You know, people just-- they were spent.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "We were so hungry, as you can imagine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "We were so thirsty.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And that filth state, it was just unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we arrived somewhere.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And as the train drew into this somewhere, and we were trying to see, naturally, someone saw the word Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, an incredible scream went up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So obviously, a lot of people did know where we were.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
